<h1>News Posts</h1><h3>News&nbsp;Permissions</h3><p>Anyone can create a news post, provided they are logged into the Josephine Butler College JCR Website.</p><h3>Creating&nbsp;A&nbsp;News Post</h3><p>News posts are now tied to events, this means that to create a news post you need to have an event associated with it. To create a news post go to the page for that event, where you will see options to create a news post for that event.</p><h3>Managing A&nbsp;News Post</h3><p>Website Admins and the News Post creator are the only people able to delete a news post.</p>